nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 175 is the 153rd issue of Star Wars Insider magazine and the eighty-third issue published by Titan Magazines. It was released on September 5, 2017. This was the first Star Wars Insider issue to feature Will Salmon as editor, succeeding Jonathan Wilkins.
Features the very best interviews and articles about the greatest space adventure of all time! Discover amazing features you never knew! Insider is the ultimate guide to the timeless saga!
